                <h1>Combatting Deforestation: Saving Our Planet</h1>
                <p>Deforestation is the large-scale removal of trees from forests, leading to severe environmental damage. It disrupts ecosystems, contributes to climate change, and threatens biodiversity. The primary causes include agriculture, logging, and urban expansion. Urgent action is needed to promote sustainable practices and reforestation efforts.</p>
